*NERVBarIcom: Title "工作区"
*NERVBarIcom: TitleButton sunkedge
*NERVBarIcom: IconButton up
*NERVBarIcom: Format "%i"
*NERVBarIcom: Tips needed
*NERVBarIcom: TipsColorset 102
*NERVBarIcom: TipsDelays 300 300
*NERVBarIcom: TipsPlacement leftright
*NERVBarIcom: ReliefThickness 1
*NERVBarIcom: Relief 1
*NERVBarIcom: ButtonGeometry x30
*NERVBarIcom: Font "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
