*NERVBarIcom: StatusFont "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*NERVBarIcom: Action Mouse 3 A sendcommand "Popup mnuWindowRight Mouse 100 100"

Read $./taskbar.icom.terminals

DestroyFunc onNERVClicked
AddToFunc onNERVClicked
+ I Popup mnuStartup Root 206p 0
+ C Nop
+ H Nop
+ M Nop

