  CirculateSkip, StaysOn, FixedPosition, FixedSize, !Iconifiable
DestroyModuleConfig NERVBar: *
*NERVBar: Geometry 205x768+0+0
*NERVBar: Rows 60
*NERVBar: Columns 1
*NERVBar: Frame 1
*NERVBar: (1x5, Back #FC0 Icon banner.png Action(Mouse 1) `onNERVClicked`)
*NERVBar: (1x30,Back #CCC Top Swallow "NERVBarIcom" "Module FvwmIconMan NERVBarIcom")
*NERVBar: (1x19,Back #CCC Top Swallow "NERVTerminalsIcom" "Module FvwmIconMan NERVTerminalsIcom")
*NERVBar: (1x2, Back #CCC Left Swallow (NoClose, UseOld) `stalonetray` `Exec exec stalonetray`)
*NERVBar: (1x3, Swallow "xclock" "exec xclock -digital -update 1 -strftime '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'")

